{"type":null,"faqId":9435,"title":"荣耀X1（7D-501u）7.0  是否可以作为 WLAN 热点？怎么操作？","answer":"<p>\n\t<span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">支持数据业务的荣耀</span><span> X1 7.0 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">可以作为</span><span> WLAN </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">热点。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>您可以参考如下步骤进行设置：</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span><span>1.</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">在主屏幕上点击</span> <img alt=\"\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=29905\" /></span><b><span></span></b><span><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">设置</span></b><span> &gt; </span><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">全部设置</span></b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span><span>2.</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">在<b>无线和网络</b>区域，点击<b>更多</b></span><b><span>…</span></b><span> &gt; </span><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">移动网络共享</span></b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=29907\" /></span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span><span>3.</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">勾选<b>便携式</b></span><b><span> WLAN </span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">热点</span></b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">后的复选框开启热点功能。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=29908\" /></span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">&nbsp;</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span><span>4.</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></span><span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">点击<b>配置</b></span><b><span> WLAN </span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">热点</span></b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">，然后根据界面显示配置您的无线局域网网络名称、密码等信息。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=29909\" /></span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">&nbsp;</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">配置完成后，其他需要上网的无线设备可以搜索并连接至荣耀</span><span> X1 7.0 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">提供的</span><span> WLAN </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">热点。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"></span></span>&nbsp;\n</p>","faqTypeId":170,"faqType":"网络与数据共享","useful":5,"unUseful":2,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"32","faqTypeCode":"Tablet-Internet-Data-Sharing","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1396252732000,"seriesProductName":"7D-501u","visitedTimes":146,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":43,"times":13,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"3","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"热点","avgScore":3.3,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}